description:
Death is a painful experience. Separation through death is one of the most tragic and difficult things that we human beings experience, and at Jesus Second Coming, this will be reversed. At His Second Coming, there will be new life. #Adventistbeliefs

To watch the full episode, paste the link into your browser: https://youtu.be/VS6LDLKtrzY
